name: XV Anniversary Gift Box (Omega)

This box contains the following: 1x Apotheosis 1x Sunesis 1x Gnosis 1x Praxis 1x Wings of Victory Firework 1x Men's Capsuleer Elite XV T-Shirt 1x Men's Capsuleer Elite XV Cap 1x Women's Capsuleer Elite XV T-Shirt 1x Women's Capsuleer Elite XV Cap 1x Apotheosis Capsuleer Elite XV SKIN 1x Sunesis Capsuleer Elite XV SKIN 1x Gnosis Capsuleer Elite XV SKIN 1x Praxis Capsuleer Elite XV SKIN 1x Capsule Capsuleer Elite XV SKIN
